      "17": "Let|strong=\"H5414\"the|strong=\"H5921\"priests|strong=\"H3548\", the|strong=\"H5921\"ministers|strong=\"H8334\"of|strong=\"H3068\"the|strong=\"H5921\"LORD|strong=\"H3068\", weep|strong=\"H1058\"between|strong=\"H5921\"the|strong=\"H5921\"porch and|strong=\"H3068\"the|strong=\"H5921\"altar|strong=\"H4196\", and|strong=\"H3068\"let|strong=\"H5414\"them|strong=\"H5414\"say, “Spare|strong=\"H2347\"your|strong=\"H3068\"people|strong=\"H5971\", LORD|strong=\"H3068\", and|strong=\"H3068\"don’t give|strong=\"H5414\"your|strong=\"H3068\"heritage|strong=\"H5159\"to|strong=\"H3068\"reproach|strong=\"H2781\", that|strong=\"H5971\"the|strong=\"H5921\"nations|strong=\"H1471\"should|strong=\"H3068\"rule|strong=\"H4910\"over|strong=\"H5921\"them|strong=\"H5414\". Why|strong=\"H4100\"should|strong=\"H3068\"they|strong=\"H3068\"say among|strong=\"H5921\"the|strong=\"H5921\"peoples|strong=\"H5971\", ‘Where|strong=\"H4100\"is|strong=\"H3068\"their|strong=\"H3068\"God|strong=\"H3068\"?’”",
      "18": "Then|strong=\"H3068\"the|strong=\"H5921\"LORD|strong=\"H3068\"was|strong=\"H3068\"jealous|strong=\"H7065\"for|strong=\"H5921\"his|strong=\"H3068\"land, and|strong=\"H3068\"had|strong=\"H3068\"pity|strong=\"H2550\"on|strong=\"H5921\"his|strong=\"H3068\"people|strong=\"H5971\".",
      "19": "The|strong=\"H5414\"LORD|strong=\"H3068\"answered|strong=\"H6030\"his|strong=\"H5414\"people|strong=\"H5971\", “Behold|strong=\"H2005\", I|strong=\"H2005\"will|strong=\"H3068\"send|strong=\"H7971\"you|strong=\"H5414\"grain|strong=\"H1715\", new|strong=\"H8492\"wine|strong=\"H8492\", and|strong=\"H3068\"oil|strong=\"H3323\", and|strong=\"H3068\"you|strong=\"H5414\"will|strong=\"H3068\"be|strong=\"H3808\"satisfied|strong=\"H7646\"with|strong=\"H7646\"them|strong=\"H5414\"; and|strong=\"H3068\"I|strong=\"H2005\"will|strong=\"H3068\"no|strong=\"H3808\"more|strong=\"H5750\"make|strong=\"H5414\"you|strong=\"H5414\"a|strong=\"H3068\"reproach|strong=\"H2781\"among|strong=\"H2781\"the|strong=\"H5414\"nations|strong=\"H1471\".",
      "20": "But|strong=\"H3588\"I|strong=\"H3588\"will|strong=\"H3220\"remove|strong=\"H7368\"the|strong=\"H6440\"northern|strong=\"H6830\"army|strong=\"H5927\"far|strong=\"H7368\"away|strong=\"H5080\"from|strong=\"H6440\"you|strong=\"H3588\", and|strong=\"H6440\"will|strong=\"H3220\"drive|strong=\"H5080\"it|strong=\"H5921\"into|strong=\"H5927\"a|strong=\"H3068\"barren|strong=\"H6723\"and|strong=\"H6440\"desolate|strong=\"H8077\"land|strong=\"H6440\", its|strong=\"H5921\"front|strong=\"H6440\"into|strong=\"H5927\"the|strong=\"H6440\"eastern|strong=\"H6931\"sea|strong=\"H3220\", and|strong=\"H6440\"its|strong=\"H5921\"back|strong=\"H5927\"into|strong=\"H5927\"the|strong=\"H6440\"western|strong=\"H3220\"sea|strong=\"H3220\"; and|strong=\"H6440\"its|strong=\"H5921\"stench will|strong=\"H3220\"come|strong=\"H5927\"up|strong=\"H5927\", and|strong=\"H6440\"its|strong=\"H5921\"bad smell|strong=\"H6709\"will|strong=\"H3220\"rise|strong=\"H5927\".” Surely|strong=\"H3588\"he|strong=\"H3588\"has|strong=\"H3588\"done|strong=\"H6213\"great|strong=\"H1431\"things|strong=\"H1431\".",
      "21": "Land, don’t be|strong=\"H3068\"afraid|strong=\"H3372\". Be|strong=\"H3068\"glad|strong=\"H8055\"and|strong=\"H3068\"rejoice|strong=\"H8055\", for|strong=\"H3588\"the|strong=\"H3588\"LORD|strong=\"H3068\"has|strong=\"H3068\"done|strong=\"H6213\"great|strong=\"H1431\"things|strong=\"H1431\".",
      "22": "Don’t be|strong=\"H5414\"afraid|strong=\"H3372\", you|strong=\"H5414\"animals of|strong=\"H7704\"the|strong=\"H3588\"field|strong=\"H7704\"; for|strong=\"H3588\"the|strong=\"H3588\"pastures|strong=\"H4999\"of|strong=\"H7704\"the|strong=\"H3588\"wilderness|strong=\"H4057\"spring|strong=\"H1876\"up|strong=\"H5375\", for|strong=\"H3588\"the|strong=\"H3588\"tree|strong=\"H6086\"bears|strong=\"H5375\"its|strong=\"H5414\"fruit|strong=\"H6529\". The|strong=\"H3588\"fig|strong=\"H8384\"tree|strong=\"H6086\"and|strong=\"H6086\"the|strong=\"H3588\"vine|strong=\"H1612\"yield|strong=\"H5414\"their|strong=\"H5375\"strength|strong=\"H2428\".",
      "23": "“Be|strong=\"H3068\"glad|strong=\"H8055\"then|strong=\"H5414\", you|strong=\"H3588\"children|strong=\"H1121\"of|strong=\"H1121\"Zion|strong=\"H6726\", and|strong=\"H1121\"rejoice|strong=\"H8055\"in|strong=\"H3068\"the|strong=\"H3588\"LORD|strong=\"H3068\", your|strong=\"H3068\"God|strong=\"H3068\"; for|strong=\"H3588\"he|strong=\"H3588\"gives|strong=\"H5414\"you|strong=\"H3588\"the|strong=\"H3588\"early|strong=\"H4175\"rain|strong=\"H1653\"in|strong=\"H3068\"just|strong=\"H6666\"measure, and|strong=\"H1121\"he|strong=\"H3588\"causes|strong=\"H5414\"the|strong=\"H3588\"rain|strong=\"H1653\"to|strong=\"H3381\"come|strong=\"H3381\"down|strong=\"H3381\"for|strong=\"H3588\"you|strong=\"H3588\", the|strong=\"H3588\"early|strong=\"H4175\"rain|strong=\"H1653\"and|strong=\"H1121\"the|strong=\"H3588\"latter|strong=\"H4456\"rain|strong=\"H1653\", as|strong=\"H3068\"before|strong=\"H7223\".",
      "24": "The|strong=\"H4390\"threshing|strong=\"H1637\"floors|strong=\"H1637\"will|strong=\"H3342\"be full|strong=\"H4390\"of|strong=\"H4390\"wheat|strong=\"H1250\", and|strong=\"H8492\"the|strong=\"H4390\"vats|strong=\"H3342\"will|strong=\"H3342\"overflow|strong=\"H7783\"with|strong=\"H4390\"new|strong=\"H8492\"wine|strong=\"H8492\"and|strong=\"H8492\"oil|strong=\"H3323\".",
      "25": "I|strong=\"H8141\"will|strong=\"H2428\"restore|strong=\"H7999\"to|strong=\"H7971\"you|strong=\"H7971\"the|strong=\"H7971\"years|strong=\"H8141\"that|strong=\"H8141\"the|strong=\"H7971\"swarming locust|strong=\"H3218\"has|strong=\"H3218\"eaten, the|strong=\"H7971\"great|strong=\"H1419\"locust|strong=\"H3218\", the|strong=\"H7971\"grasshopper|strong=\"H2625\", and|strong=\"H7971\"the|strong=\"H7971\"caterpillar|strong=\"H2625\", my|strong=\"H7971\"great|strong=\"H1419\"army|strong=\"H2428\", which|strong=\"H2428\"I|strong=\"H8141\"sent|strong=\"H7971\"among you|strong=\"H7971\".",
      "26": "You|strong=\"H6213\"will|strong=\"H3068\"have|strong=\"H3068\"plenty|strong=\"H7646\"to|strong=\"H3068\"eat and|strong=\"H3068\"be|strong=\"H3808\"satisfied|strong=\"H7646\", and|strong=\"H3068\"will|strong=\"H3068\"praise|strong=\"H1984\"the|strong=\"H6213\"name|strong=\"H8034\"of|strong=\"H3068\"the|strong=\"H6213\"LORD|strong=\"H3068\", your|strong=\"H3068\"God|strong=\"H3068\", who|strong=\"H5971\"has|strong=\"H3068\"dealt|strong=\"H6213\"wondrously|strong=\"H6381\"with|strong=\"H5973\"you|strong=\"H6213\"; and|strong=\"H3068\"my|strong=\"H3068\"people|strong=\"H5971\"will|strong=\"H3068\"never|strong=\"H3808\"again be|strong=\"H3808\"disappointed.",
      "27": "You|strong=\"H3588\"will|strong=\"H3068\"know|strong=\"H3045\"that|strong=\"H3588\"I|strong=\"H3588\"am|strong=\"H3068\"among|strong=\"H7130\"Israel|strong=\"H3478\", and|strong=\"H3478\"that|strong=\"H3588\"I|strong=\"H3588\"am|strong=\"H3068\"the|strong=\"H3588\"LORD|strong=\"H3068\", your|strong=\"H3068\"God|strong=\"H3068\", and|strong=\"H3478\"there|strong=\"H3045\"is|strong=\"H3068\"no|strong=\"H3808\"one|strong=\"H3808\"else|strong=\"H5750\"; and|strong=\"H3478\"my|strong=\"H3068\"people|strong=\"H5971\"will|strong=\"H3068\"never|strong=\"H3808\"again|strong=\"H5750\"be|strong=\"H5750\"disappointed.",
      "28": "“It will happen afterward, that I will pour out my Spirit on all flesh; and your sons and your daughters will prophesy. Your old men will dream dreams. Your young men will see visions.",
      "29": "And also on the servants and on the handmaids in those days, I will pour out my Spirit.",
      "30": "I will show wonders in the heavens and in the earth: blood, fire, and pillars of smoke.",
      "31": "The sun will be turned into darkness, and the moon into blood, before the great and terrible day of the LORD|strong=\"H3068\"comes.",
      "32": "It will happen that whoever will call on the LORD|strong=\"H3068\"’s name shall be saved; for in Mount Zion and in Jerusalem there will be those who escape, as the LORD|strong=\"H3068\"has said, and among the remnant, those whom the LORD|strong=\"H3068\"calls."
    },
    "3": {
      "1": "“For|strong=\"H5921\", behold|strong=\"H7200\", in|strong=\"H5921\"those|strong=\"H3605\"days, and|strong=\"H1121\"in|strong=\"H5921\"that|strong=\"H7200\"time|strong=\"H1961\", when|strong=\"H1961\"I|strong=\"H5921\"restore|strong=\"H2492\"the|strong=\"H3605\"fortunes of|strong=\"H1121\"Judah and|strong=\"H1121\"Jerusalem,",
      "2": "I|strong=\"H3117\"will|strong=\"H5650\"gather all|strong=\"H3117\"nations, and|strong=\"H3117\"will|strong=\"H5650\"bring them|strong=\"H1992\"down|strong=\"H5921\"into|strong=\"H5921\"the|strong=\"H5921\"valley of|strong=\"H3117\"Jehoshaphat; and|strong=\"H3117\"I|strong=\"H3117\"will|strong=\"H5650\"execute judgment on|strong=\"H5921\"them|strong=\"H1992\"there|strong=\"H1992\"for|strong=\"H5921\"my|strong=\"H5921\"people|strong=\"H1571\", and|strong=\"H3117\"for|strong=\"H5921\"my|strong=\"H5921\"heritage, Israel, whom|strong=\"H1992\"they|strong=\"H1992\"have|strong=\"H1571\"scattered among|strong=\"H5921\"the|strong=\"H5921\"nations. They|strong=\"H1992\"have|strong=\"H1571\"divided my|strong=\"H5921\"land,",
      "3": "and|strong=\"H8064\"have|strong=\"H5414\"cast|strong=\"H5414\"lots for|strong=\"H5414\"my|strong=\"H5414\"people|strong=\"H1818\", and|strong=\"H8064\"have|strong=\"H5414\"given|strong=\"H5414\"a|strong=\"H3068\"boy for|strong=\"H5414\"a|strong=\"H3068\"prostitute, and|strong=\"H8064\"sold a|strong=\"H3068\"girl for|strong=\"H5414\"wine, that|strong=\"H5414\"they|strong=\"H5414\"may|strong=\"H5414\"drink.",
      "4": "“Yes, and|strong=\"H3068\"what|strong=\"H3372\"are|strong=\"H3117\"you|strong=\"H6440\"to|strong=\"H3068\"me|strong=\"H6440\", Tyre and|strong=\"H3068\"Sidon, and|strong=\"H3068\"all|strong=\"H1419\"the|strong=\"H6440\"regions of|strong=\"H3068\"Philistia? Will|strong=\"H3068\"you|strong=\"H6440\"repay me|strong=\"H6440\"? And|strong=\"H3068\"if you|strong=\"H6440\"repay me|strong=\"H6440\", I|strong=\"H3117\"will|strong=\"H3068\"swiftly and|strong=\"H3068\"speedily return your|strong=\"H3068\"repayment on|strong=\"H3117\"your|strong=\"H3068\"own|strong=\"H6440\"head|strong=\"H6440\".",
      "5": "Because|strong=\"H3588\"you|strong=\"H3588\"have|strong=\"H1961\"taken|strong=\"H1961\"my|strong=\"H3605\"silver and|strong=\"H3068\"my|strong=\"H3605\"gold, and|strong=\"H3068\"have|strong=\"H1961\"carried|strong=\"H3068\"my|strong=\"H3605\"finest treasures into|strong=\"H1961\"your|strong=\"H3068\"temples,",
      "6": "and have sold the children of Judah and the children of Jerusalem to the sons of the Greeks, that you may remove them far from their border.",
      "7": "Behold, I will stir them up out of the place where you have sold them, and will return your repayment on your own head;",
      "8": "and I will sell your sons and your daughters into the hands of the children of Judah, and they will sell them to the men of Sheba, to a|strong=\"H3068\"faraway nation, for the LORD|strong=\"H3068\"has spoken it.”",
      "9": "Proclaim this among the nations: “Prepare for war! Stir up the mighty men. Let all the warriors draw near. Let them come up.",
      "10": "Beat your plowshares into swords, and your pruning hooks into spears. Let the weak say, ‘I am strong.’",
      "11": "Hurry and come, all you surrounding nations, and gather yourselves together.” Cause your mighty ones to come down there, LORD|strong=\"H3068\".",
      "12": "“Let the nations arouse themselves, and come up to the valley of Jehoshaphat; for there I will sit to judge all the surrounding nations.",
      "13": "Put in the sickle; for the harvest is ripe. Come, tread, for the wine press is full, the vats overflow, for their wickedness is great.”",
      "14": "Multitudes, multitudes in the valley of decision! For the day of the LORD|strong=\"H3068\"is near in the valley of decision.",
      "15": "The sun and the moon are darkened, and the stars withdraw their shining.",
      "16": "The LORD|strong=\"H3068\"will roar from Zion, and thunder from Jerusalem; and the heavens and the earth will shake; but the LORD|strong=\"H3068\"will be a|strong=\"H3068\"refuge to his people, and a|strong=\"H3068\"stronghold to the children of Israel.",
      "17": "“So you will know that I am the LORD|strong=\"H3068\", your God, dwelling in Zion, my holy mountain. Then Jerusalem will be holy, and no strangers will pass through her any more.",
      "18": "It will happen in that day, that the mountains will drop down sweet wine, the hills will flow with milk, all the brooks of Judah will flow with waters; and a|strong=\"H3068\"fountain will flow out from the LORD|strong=\"H3068\"’s house, and will water the valley of Shittim.",
      "19": "Egypt will be a|strong=\"H3068\"desolation and Edom will be a|strong=\"H3068\"desolate wilderness, for the violence done to the children of Judah, because they have shed innocent blood in their land.",
      "20": "But Judah will be inhabited forever, and Jerusalem from generation to generation.",
      "21": "I will cleanse their blood that I have not cleansed, for the LORD|strong=\"H3068\"dwells in Zion.”"
    }
  }
}